{"tid":950202,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"恭賀麥巴比20歲生日　認定對方新比利","createTime":"2018-12-21T10:38:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T10:50:59.000Z","uid":1121,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e02e6664c2d05cd857a227803a1faee4f5ee6d64","tid":950202,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T10:38:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181221/s00006/1f7337d2ce7691f58a57ff515ff88ac1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181221%2Fs00006%2F1f7337d2ce7691f58a57ff515ff88ac1.jpg&h=975541c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法國新星基利安麥巴比昨日步入20歲，獲得不少恭賀，當中包括已78歲的巴西球王比利。後者認為麥巴比今夏能贏得世界盃，他日成就能媲美自己。<br />\n<br />\n比利60年前協助巴西贏得1958年世界盃，當年他只有17歲，而麥巴比今夏也不足20歲稱雄世盃，比利在網上發帖稱：「只有奇才這麼早表現到自己。生日快樂，基利安。20歲的時光，我對未來的憧憬感到興奮。」他早幾日接受法國傳媒訪問時說「麥巴比會是新比利，巴黎聖日耳門打出水準應可晉身歐聯決賽。」比利又在網上談到35年前雷米金盃被盜一事，笑說自己至少在失竊前，曾與獎盃共度美好時光。"},{"pid":"d26ff229c4934facff674f0e0818f50cb1aff836","tid":950202,"uid":60432,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T10:39:07.000Z","msg":"麥巴比慘"},{"pid":"b5bb40a719cf831840b6e0140500886f44d55922","tid":950202,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T10:39:10.000Z","msg":"又少粒新星"},{"pid":"bcdd29d47b2acfef778952a46c2b9d7f89306223","tid":950202,"uid":64181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T10:39:51.000Z","msg":"又燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981b440a4865ae5bc8ecbd8cb4aa0d5d51cb5a3f","tid":950202,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d26ff229c4934facff674f0e0818f50cb1aff836","tid":950202,"uid":60432,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T10:39:07.000Z","msg":"麥巴比慘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T10:40:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\